{"tid":1794704,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"林兆波唔肯食餃子 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-12-23T10:13:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T10:14:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2326ad1993a32cc75eaa2ee86e59945deb70dc05","tid":1794704,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T10:13:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191223/20829919/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191223%2F20829919%2F&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwTIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=5e6366ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191223%2F20829919%2F&h=142c1534\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191223/20829919/</a><br />\n<br />\n林兆波唔肯食餃子 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191223/large/1577000326_a532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191223%2Flarge%2F1577000326_a532.jpg&h=416929fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n楊天命預測，未來好多高官走佬，將會好大變化。明年三月，香港有個人出現，這個人好犀利，到時有可能變天。<br />\n<br />\n半信半疑之際，澳門傳來動畫，全部契弟迎合甴總歌唱祖國時拍爛手掌千人一面的畫像中，一夫當關的林兆波兄，遺世獨立左手緊按右手。手，唔係用來拍馬屁嘅。握完甴總的手，波兄死命按着滲透全身火燒感那個Pepe冏樣，令網民起哄，封林兆波做前線手足。高調表態不合作勁勇武啊，拒絕行埋的波兄，極可能是楊天命預言三月變天的關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n有五五波機會成為真命天子，波兄身邊的林奠，拍住手歌唱但明顯已經睄到枕邊人「不按本子辦事」。鏡頭捕捉到，林奠那副尊容，難頂過後母。家不和，萬事難興，內外交困的林奠，過唔到人間三月天，一點唔奇。<br />\n<br />\n林兆波罷拍賀馬交，老婆同是姓奠的潘某假如站在前排，會露出柒樣嗎？直送國家首都，強制「食餃子」，是甴總明年整治香港高官上演插翼難飛重頭戲的吉時。高官爭住跳船的海難畫面， 有人已預先鼓掌。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"19c47072456ca9afe963ba2b00704d1557f4f9bb","tid":1794704,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T10:14:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">稅局聖誕激光燈飾之夜</span><br />\n19:00<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「星火不息 燃點國際」集會</span><br />\n日期︰2019年12月23日(一)<br />\n時間︰晚上七時至九時<br />\n地點︰中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n主辦方︰張崑陽、候任中西區區議員梁晃維、民間集會團隊<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">已獲警方發出不反對通知書</span>"},{"pid":"6b4b4033cf58fc03a81cd6a347fb830345f6679f","tid":1794704,"uid":88940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T10:14:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/xmasevehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fxmasevehk&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwTIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=56050b8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/xmasevehk</a><br />\n唔好意思借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟攬炒！香港人果七千萬比人搞啊！佢老母仲OT成九億<br />\n1224<br />\n1225<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[行動] [推上熱門] 我宣佈 聽日平安夜攬炒正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794689</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}